External Knowledge:
- "harmony between the voices of the LR and RF models" refers to the average correlation between the Linear Regression (LR) and Random Forest (RF) models; 
- "active singer" means a user with 'is_active' flag set to 1; 
- "performed in multiple concerts" means having more than one correlation_id.

sql:
SELECT MAX(training_date) AS most_recent_training_date
FROM (
    SELECT training_date FROM lr_models
    UNION
    SELECT training_date FROM rf_models
);

SELECT date, response_time
FROM conversations
ORDER BY date DESC;
